    "Name": "BattleMaster",
    "Details": "Another Kuritan 'Mech that was built to utilize C3 technology, the K3 BattleMaster was introduced the same year as the CM but uses an XL engine. The 'Mech is armed with an ER PPC and two ER large lasers for long-range combat with four ER medium lasers and a Streak SRM-6 launcher for close combat situations. Finally, the 'Mech carries a single C3 master computer.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Command Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
